**For Postman with API Key and JWT:
Go to Body with this Input: {"email" : "example@example.ch" , "password" : "Bfo12345"}
Send it as post with this path: http://localhost:8080/auth/jwt
You will get an Token
Go to an post with this path: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/todos
Go to Authorization and put Bearer Token in and paste the Token in now do Get